title: John Burnet of Barns: A Romance
author: Buchan, John
snippet: Soon I came to the small, roofless shieling of Redshaw, where aforetimelived a villain of rare notoriety, with whose name, "Redshaw Jock," JeanMorran embittered my childhood.
